[VIBE] (GUILD VIBE, GUILD TELL)

  Communicates a message to everyone in who is logged on in the guild.

Usage:  vibe <msg>
        vibe :<msg>
        vibe [list, muffle]

Parameters:

 <msg>     Echoes the message <msg> to everyone in the guild.

 :<msg>     Echoes the emotion <msg> to everyone in the guild.

 list      Lists all the people currently on the guild channel.

 muffle    Toggles the channel on/off. (toggle muffle) is the same thing.

 history   Displays a recent list of discussion on the guild channel.
 
>> This command is the same as 'guild vibe' and 'guild tell'.
